{"type": "article", "id": 5039, "title": "Hash 模块化书架", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-08T08:04:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233630RaqfJ3N0heXoQLsw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自乌克兰设计工作室 Line 的设计师 Max Voytenko 日前推出一款模块化书架作品 Hash，其最大的特点在于可以进行自由组合，拼出不同的风格与样式，以适应不同大小的房间与环境。Hash 的一面是黑色的实心钢板，其余三面则由黑色的片钢制造出可视化又分割视线的挡板，可以自转 90度，看起来颇有几分炫酷之感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233628WoYhzLZt7blOAmpB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233628Uv0CtFBQ2LHkdPli.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233629wHhoDsSXIELj4cQK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233629C6gRPcoG23xuH0aJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233629oknKW0lPNJ9Da62m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}